title: 'GAME OF TROLLS' CLUB CANT SEE MY OWN CLUB????
body:
CAN SOMEONE HELP ALREADY? WHY IS THIS A THING?? 
I am the maker of the club and cant fucking see it. Been trying to ask for help since last year....WAITING ~{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}}

replies.body:
Hey there,

>Been trying to ask for help since last year....WAITING ~

I'm terribly sorry to hear that, however I cannot find any previous threads from you about this issue.

This is a simple fix, however you're going to have to [go through Player Support](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) as we here on the boards are unable to assist with account specific issues.
so as usual " send a ticked and we will ignore it"
